  <brief_title>Temozolomide and Concomitant Whole Brain Radiotherapy in NSCLC Patients With Brain Metastases</brief_title>
  <official_title>Temozolomide and Concomitant Whole Brain Radiotherapy in NSCLC Patients With Brain Metastases: A Randomized Trial</official_title>
